NYTimes article of Sept 13, 1914: 
headline: <b>Rutt Goes Back to Fight</b>
&quot;Champion Cyclist Leaves Newark to Join the Kaiser's Army&quot;
&quot; <b>Walter Rutt</b>, the German cyclist and ,<b>world's champion</b> of 1914, has suddenly disappeared and is probably now on the high seas bound for Europe to get in touch with one of the German armies.&quot;
